  <button type="button" class="collapsible"><img src="{{course-files-path}}/img/crabster.jpg" style="height: 25px" /> 
  &nbsp; Can't figure this exercise out? Click here to open a MatCrab workspace to help you.</button>
  <div class="content">
    <p> <br>
    MatCrab can help you check your work, if you would like. 
    {{#text-area}}(To get it to show the result, make sure to store your result in a variable, e.g. <code>{{text-area}}</code>.){{/text-area}}
    {{^text-area}}{{/text-area}}
  </p>
{{/collapsible}}
